TLDR: Fill out this form to volunteer for the Berkeley Math Tournament (BMT) and get free food!: https://forms.gle/oy5DipwJ8nsb7iK2A

Hello Everyone! The Berkeley Math Tournament (BMT) is hosting its first online tournament for the Bay Area. We have over 1000 people across the US and the world registered to take our tournament. The tournament will be taking place in two weeks on October 3rd and 4th. We are looking for volunteers who are willing to help out from 12:30 - 4:30 PM PST on October 3rd. Volunteers will be reimbursed 30$ for food costs for Lunch and Dinner on October 3rd. Please fill out the below form to sign up!

https://forms.gle/oy5DipwJ8nsb7iK2A
history.subject: Berkeley Math Tournament (BMT) Volunteer - Get Free Food!
